                                                                        <div id="elementor-tab-content-2206" class="elementor-tab-content elementor-clearfix" data-tab="6" role="tabpanel" aria-labelledby="elementor-tab-title-2206">
                                                                            <p>Yes, customers can now call to voicemail through RVM. It allows you to send a voicemail call directly into the voicemail inbox of your prospect. Ringless Voicemail Drops are sent directly from your device server to your prospect’s server.</p>
                                                                            <p>It will display as a miss call alert on the device of the recipient. You can also broadcast voice on mobile or landline directly. The RVM also helps you in sales and marketing.</p>
